      <p><a href="ch73s13.html#MonstersAnimals42">Crocodiles</a> are aggressive predators 11 to 12 feet long. They lie mostly submerged in rivers or marshes, with only their eyes and nostrils showing, waiting for prey to come within reach.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2279334"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
